{"type": "article", "id": 14052, "title": "盛放肥皂的皂云", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-27T07:48:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000306L8TOV7hxWJGdK3aR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t肥皂容易烂软在盒子里，尤其是潮湿的地方。来自台湾的茸毛工作室设计了一个保护肥皂的皂云，直径 10 厘米，采用硅胶材质，接触其表面的水分会露珠化最终顺着下水道迅速流出。越用越小的肥皂也能在这个装置的帮助下聚成圆形，维持肥皂的寿命。产品目前刚刚结束集资，预计 9 月份可以出售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141656t5bJGWpwRzDyjxNU.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"686\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.8575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141657WjSPsb1DH8yAhCOi.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"262\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.3275\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261416579Bzh5NklXoWQSH2b.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"375\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.46875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141657EkNdwmzK8Di0uTxa.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}